      <p id="Par34">In Fig.Â <xref rid="Fig1" ref-type="fig">1</xref>b (left panel) we show a simulated tumour where after <inline-formula id="IEq48"><alternatives><tex-math id="M109">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
