      <p id="Par41">Model confidence and stability can be formalized using bootstrap procedures. In Fig.Â <xref rid="Fig3" ref-type="fig">3</xref> we show the result of a non-parametric bootstrap run with 200 resamples, which can be used to estimate bootstrap confidence intervals (CI) for all the model parameters at a desired <inline-formula id="IEq66"><alternatives><tex-math id="M149">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
